author: Yasser Ghoneim
title: Yasser Ghoneim
text:
I purchased tickets for some football matches in london and the process was very easy and the safety check made me feel am safe, but i have to say am a bit worried as am traveling to london on friday and the games are on Tuesday & Wednesday and i didn't receive anything so far, is this normal? am traveling mainly for these 2 games so please confirm ill receive tickets as purchased
Thank you and i hope you don't let me down
